import React from 'react'
import { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap'


import Header from '../components/Header'
import Footer from '../components/Footer';

const SharedLayout = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Header />
            
            <main className='py-3'>
                <Container>
                    <Outlet />
                </Container>
            </main>
        <Footer />  
    </>  
          )
}

export default SharedLayout
